headline: Restaurant sector playbook: Stocks to buy & avoid
summary: Jacob Aiken-Phillips, Melius Research vice president of consumer and retail research, joins Market Domination to explain why he believes McDonald's (MCD) and Starbucks (SBUX) pricing no longer match the value consumers expect. Watch the video above to hear Aiken-Phillips explain why Dutch Bros (BROS) still looks like a Buy.
